data.description: *** QUALIFIES FOR  ZERO DOWN FINANCING -USDA ***. FHA appraisal completed*** Back on market due to buyer financing.*** 3 Beautiful open acres with no HOA! Fully renovated in 2015, this one level all brick rambler features a brand new 3 bay garage, large shed  and a fenced field.  So many opportunities with this much open space! . This home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths with updated roof, windows, appliances, granite counter tops and brand new kitchen flooring just installed! Real hardwood floors throughout. New water heater 2023!   Brand new Heat pump  in December 2019 and Gutters on front of home in 2021. Xfinity/comcast available.  Call or email today to schedule your showing!
